MotoIntel AI
Predictive Diagnostic Interface for Smart Vehicles
Developed by PrAv
Technical Overview
MotoIntel AI is an intelligent diagnostic telemetry system designed to evaluate mechanical reliability in real time. By continuously analyzing engine parameters across thermal, vibrational, and electrical domains, the system computes a dynamic Health Index that reflects overall vehicle condition.
System Architecture
Interface: Streamlit (Python-based UI)
Analytics Engine: Neural-Threshold Matrix Model
Hardware Integration: ESP32 with IoT Connectivity
Current Status
Operational — Version 1.0
